item.title: CVE-2020-2265|2024-08-04T07:01:41.215Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20coverage%2Fcomplexity%20scatter%20plot%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Coverage/Complexity Scatter Plot Plugin 1.1.1 and earlier does not escape the method information in tooltips, resulting in a stored cross-site scripting (XSS) vulnerability exploitable by attackers able to provide report files to the plugin's post-build step.
